cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with vehicle detection and tracking in driving scenarios using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and autonomous driving, which suggests the category cs.RO (Robotics). The use of deep learning techniques for vehicle detection and tracking also indicates the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for text summarization, which suggests the category cs.CL (Computation and Language).
